<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4745753>
    dc:description "FIGURE 31. Microtrombicula fulgida (Schluger, Grochovskaja, Ngu, Hoe and Tung, 1963), lectotype. A, anterior part of idiosoma, dorsal aspect; B, anterior part of idiosoma, ventral aspect. Microtrombicula vitosa (Schluger, Grochovskaja, Ngu, Hoe and Tung, 1963), paralectotype ZMMU Tdt-3281 (specimen 1). C, anterior part of idiosoma, dorsal aspect; D, anterior part of idiosoma, ventral aspect. Scale bars: 100 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4745753/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4745767>
    dc:description "FIGURE 35. Microtrombicula vitosa (Schluger, Grochovskaja, Ngu, Hoe and Tung, 1963). A, arrangement of dorsal idiosomal setae of paralectotype ZMMU Tdt-3281 “Trombicula vitosa-2” (specimen 3); B, arrangement of ventral idiosomal setae of paralectotype ZMMU Tdt-3281 “Trombicula vitosa-2” (specimen 3); C, dorsal idiosomal seta of 1st row of lectotype; D, coxal seta I of paralectotype ZMMU Tdt-3280 “Trombicula vitosa-2” (specimen 1); E, coxal seta II of paralectotype ZMMU Tdt-3280 “Trombicula vitosa-2” (specimen 1); F, coxal seta III of paralectotype ZMMU Tdt-3280 “Trombicula vitosa-2” (specimen 1); G, anterior sternal seta of lectotype; H, posterior sternal seta of lectotype; I, preanal seta of lectotype. Scale bars: 100 μm (A, B), 20 μm (C–I)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4745767/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4745769>
    dc:description "FIGURE 36. Microtrombicula vitosa (Schluger, Grochovskaja, Ngu, Hoe and Tung, 1963), lectotype. A, dorsal aspect of gnathosoma; B, ventral aspect of gnathosoma; C, scutum and eyes (right sensillum and branches of left sensillum missing); D, leg I (trochanter–tarsus); E, leg II (trochanter–tarsus); F, leg III (trochanter–tarsus) (mastitarsala broken). Scale bars: 20 μm (A, B), 50 μm (C), 50 μm (D–F)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4745769/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4745775>
    dc:description "FIGURE 37. Type specimens of Microtrombicula vitosa (Schluger, Grochovskaja, Ngu, Hoe and Tung, 1963) on slides." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4745775/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

